title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (September 11 - October 8) will also receive:

— The Canis Terminus Patrol (Emergency)
— 50% off Bail Offices and their Upgrades and Modifications
— Double Rewards on Dispatch Work
— The Stun Gun at the Gun Van
— Double Rewards on Bounty Targets
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
